About Us
Our Story
Since 2000, Classic Caladiums has strived to serve the horticulture industry as well as the consumers as a reliable supplier of a diverse line of proprietary caladium varieties. Our breeding program has delivered more than 70 new caladium varieties to the market while expanding their use from traditional summer shade color. New varieties now handle full sun, and have thicker leaves making them tougher in the environment. With new looks, colors, patterns, leaf shapes, and environmental tolerances we are confident the market will continue to rapidly expand.
Meet the Classic team working to bring you the best quality caladiums possible
